      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>potatoes </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim the green stalk[s] off your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potato </strong>and <strong>aubergine </strong>to the dish and stir everything together</p>",
