    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with the lid and put the dish in the oven for 40-45 min or until the potatoes are tender and everything's cooked – this is your <strong>one-pot Greek-style meat-free mince stew</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
