    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's almost done, strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Tip: Hold the top of the herb sprigs firmly and slide your fingers down their lengths to easily remove the leaves</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> into a bowl with the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and mix together – this is your<strong> mint & feta topping</strong></p>",
