      "instruction": "<p>To serve, remove the <strong>one-pot Greek-style meat-free mince stew</strong> from the oven and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>if needed</p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> mint & feta topping</strong> all over the <strong>one-pot Greek-style meat-free mince stew</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
